<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Notebook Entry</div>
<dl id="n08125y"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n08" href="#n08125y">N08 (VI.B.6)</a>:  <a href="../../FF/fnbs/n08all.htm#n08125y"> 125(y)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> little reverence</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">In Russian monasteries the rosary is usually said five times a day, while in the recitation of it the &ldquo;great reverences&rdquo; are reduced to 10, the remainder being simply sixty &ldquo;little reverences&rdquo; (bowing of the head no further than the waist) &hellip;. <small> <a name="CECRA" href="../../FF/fdra/fdex.htm#CECRA"><cite title="source">&ldquo;Coemgen&rdquo;, &ldquo;Rosary&rdquo; and &ldquo;Albigenses&rdquo;</cite></a> <cite a>Catholic Encyclopaedia</cite></a> (1911) XIII, &lsquo;Rosary&rsquo; 188a</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
